  "title": "ACCOUNTING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>Maintain & manage full sets of accounts;</p><p>· Prepare & submit quarterly GST returns;</p><p>· Reconciliation of accounts;</p><p>· Preparing monthly management reports;</p><p>· Prepare and update collection from cash, cheques, telegrahic transfer and GIRO on a timely manner;</p><p>. Handle Petty Cash;</p><p>· Ensuring accurate and appropriate recording and analysis of revenues and expenses;</p><p>· Issuing of sales invoices;</p><p>. Filing of AIS;</p><p>· Assist in yearly audit and tax computation;</p><p>· Liaise and coordinate with external auditors and tax agents;</p><p>. Ensure accounting deadlines are met;</p><p>· Ad-hoc duties as assigned.</p>",
